accessibility.text: 🤓  Get a part-time job at a cafe to saving money!

Mom 🤔 ： \"Amy, I am happy that you want to learn an instrument. But... Why guitar? Look at the friends around you, they all know how to play the piano. Why don't you consider about learning the piano? I will only support you if you want to learn the piano.\"
Me 😀 : \"Mom! I want to learn how to play the guitar! Can you support me to buy a guitar that I like?\"
😒  Fine. I will just learn the piano instead of guitar.
